## Getting Started

1. Clone project to local folder

{% if is_python_project -%}
2. Configure conda environment:

   ```sh
   # create new environment
   mamba env create --name {{ python_import_name }} -f ./environment-dev.yaml
   python -m pip install --no-deps -r requirements.txt
   python -m pip install --no-deps -r ds_utils-requirements.txt
   # may require Azure Token when prompted for password

   # or update existing environment
   conda activate {{ python_import_name }}
   mamba env update --name {{ python_import_name }} -f ./environment.yaml
   ```

